{"tid":197310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(電競MK)之愚人節?人人都唔愚 剩係愚你?","createTime":"2017-04-11T20:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T08:33:21.000Z","uid":99218,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20c178de491bb7401c442e7c0e0bfce07db0dc3e","tid":197310,"uid":99218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:24:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>原本今日9個月紀念日 仲打左篇野出黎哄你開心<br />\n點知岩岩就比我發現左D野 係人地個FACEBOOK到睇到D咁既留言~<br />\n我知道內容唔係事實有做過 但比外人見到 人地點諗我?<br />\n我亦都知道 留言有咁多女仔唔講唔會無啦啦搵你黎講<br />\n之前已經因為同依條仔長期密密INBOX搞到我同你嘈左獲勁既~<br />\n果陣仲實牙實齒話同佢無野~仲鬧番我轉頭 屌柒我 話我咩都介意<br />\n好~ 你多次出賣我 我都信任你 交個心對你 一心一意 換黎既係咩?<br />\n件事過左幾個月 姐係而家4月12號 比我發現到你同人地係FB打埋D咁既野<br />\n之後同我講係愚人節?人人都唔愚 剩係愚你? 我諗似係你愚緊我多D,天天都是愚人節?<br />\n正常一個正常人 睇到d咁既野 咩人都有火啦<br />\n我叫你比個合理既解釋我 你唔企係我角度諗點解我咁嬲都算<br />\n仲要錄音不停屌柒我 好野 比個叻你<br />\n一齊左9個月 基本上我乜都無~無名無份~係格離睇你收兵~<br />\n你身邊D男仔既福利都好過我 我就剩係做你既柴可夫司機<br />\n晚晚接你收工 你出TRIP送你去機埸 你晚晚就同其他仔INBOX~<br />\n我就9個月以黎 無同過任何女仔曖昧 野都唔多講句<br />\n同你岩岩分完手 復合番 而家又比我發現D咁既野<br />\n其實已經唔止一次 到底我周德溎呢一生人入面 係咪真係注定比另一半出賣同背叛? <br />\n9個月以黎 同我講起碼過百次分手~ 我今次真係成全你啦 分手啦<br />\n我想同大家講 要摧毀一段感情 真係好容易~<br />\n狗公到處都是 大家有女朋友既男仔 我希望你地醒醒定定<br />\n我唔撚想再做傻仔啦 我寧願以後做隻單身狗都唔撚想成日迎住迎住帶綠帽</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c9P1a47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc9P1a47.jpg&h=328193c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHY696T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHY696T.jpg&h=08794e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QABz3G5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQABz3G5.jpg&h=bb6effe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男士主(Chow Tak Kwai)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chow.t.kwai\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchow.t.kwai&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=56ff08e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chow.t.kwai</a><br />\n<br />\n女士主(Lily Yim)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lilybbb.1997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flilybbb.1997&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f9ab81c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lilybbb.1997</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時未知比咩名份(Wing Yiu Chan)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yiuchan.wing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyiuchan.wing&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c303070d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yiuchan.wing</a><br />\n<br />\n原Link <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chow.t.kwai/posts/10155409075253641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchow.t.kwai%2Fposts%2F10155409075253641&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f9f06be6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chow.t.kwai/posts/10155409075253641</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我就唔係事主 只係放上黎比大家食下生花</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>綠帽唔怕戴 最緊要除得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"93c6ebae8f8c4935d4e288f8070d29763044865b","tid":197310,"uid":99218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Frot0x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Frot0x.jpg&h=5fd72381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1O1646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1O1646.jpg&h=0330ecb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf2dc728ed16242a7ad4d765d4b9c86817ac3bdd","tid":197310,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T